race.description: Follow Thedogssa On X Stake Ctb Division1
race.comment: TAKE A LITTLE (5) ran below her best last time finishing fifth (38.26) over 643m at Gawler in a OPEN. Form at the trip sound including two wins. Can make amends. SOUTH STAND ENVY (3) scored two back then drifted back and missed the frame latest finishing a 3.5 lengths 4th at Murray Bridge (26.12). Safe beginner who has drawn to advantage. Must be included in calculations. VICTA GRAHAM (7) goes very well this trip starting five times for two wins and two minors. Comes off a (30.91) win last time, scoring by 6 lengths in a Grade 6 over 530m at this track. Among the main chances. JOKER'S QUEEN (1) deserves plenty of thought at her first run at this distance.
